<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Home</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

  <!-- CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" />

  <!-- script -->
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <script src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.14.0/js/all.js"></script>
  <script src="./js/index.js"></script>
</head>

<body>

  <!--Navbar-->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">

    <!-- Navbar brand -->
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <a class="navbar-brand justify-content-between title" href="/">airM&M</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Burger -->
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#topHeader"
      aria-controls="topHeader" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <!-- Collapsible content -->
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse " id="topHeader">
        <ul class="navbar-nav smooth-scroll col-md-auto ml-auto">
          <li class="nav-item active">
            <a class="nav-link title" href="/">Home</a>
          </li>

          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link title" href="#promotions">Promotions</a>
          </li>

          <li class="nav-item">
            <div class="dropdown">
              <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle title" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true"
                aria-expanded="false" href="#">Become a host</a>
              <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownHost">
                <a class="dropdown-item title" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signUp" href="#">Sign Up</a>
                <a class="dropdown-item title" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#uploadListing" href="#">Upload your
                  listing</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li class="nav-item">
            <div class="dropdown">
              <button class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle signInUp" type="button" id="dropdownUser"
                data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
                <i class="fas fa-user user-icon"></i>
              </button>
              <div class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownUser">
                <a class="dropdown-item title" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signUp" href="#">Sign
                  Up</a>
                <a class="dropdown-item title" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#logIn" href="#">Log In</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </nav>

  <!-- Full Page Image Header with Vertically Centered Content -->
  <header class="masthead" id="findPlace">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row h-100">
        <div class="row col-12">

          <form class="searchForm" id="findPlaceForm" action="/rooms" method="POST" novalidate>
            <h2 class="title text-center">Find your unique places.</h2>
            <div class="form-group col-md-12">
              <hr class="hr-dark">
              <label class="form-label bookingSearchLabel" for="location">WHERE</label>
              <select id="location" class="form-control">
                <option>Toronto</option>
                <option>Vancouver</option>
                <option>Quebec</option>
                <option>Montreal</option>
                <option>Calgary</option>
                <option>Ottawa</option>
                <option>Edmonton</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group col-md-12">
              <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label bookingSearchLabel" for="checkIn">CHECK IN</label>
                  <input type="date" class="form-control" id="checkIn" required>
                  <div class="invalid-feedback">Please pick a date</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                  <label class="form-label bookingSearchLabel" for="checkOut">CHECK OUT</label>
                  <input type="date" class="form-control" id="checkOut" required>
                  <div class="invalid-feedback">Please pick a date</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group col-md-12">
              <label class="form-label bookingSearchLabel" for="inputLocation">GUESTS</label>
              <input type="number" class="form-control" id="inputLocation" min="1" placeholder="Number of guests..."
                required>
              <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter a number</div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group col-md-12">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary bookingSearch btn-block">Search</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Promotions -->
  <div id="promotions" class="container-fluid mb-0">
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center text-center">
      <h2 class="title">Promotions</h2>
    </div>

    <hr class="hr-dark">

    <div class="card-deck">
      <div class="card rounded">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="./images/selfieAd.jpg" alt="Selfie promotion">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Share your happy moment</h5>
          <p class="card-text">During your stay with us and have a chance to receive a FREE
            stay.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Last updated 3 mins ago</small></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card rounded">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="./images/winterAd.jpg" alt="Winter promotion">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Winter Promotion</h5>
          <p class="card-text">Enjoy 5% OFF all stay this winter</p>
          <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Valid through Feb 28, 2021</small></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card rounded">
        <img class="card-img-top" src="./images/friendAd.jpg" alt="Refer friends">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">Refer a friend</h5>
          <p class="card-text">And receive a 10CAD coupon applied to your next stay.</p>
          <p class="card-text"><small class="text-muted">Terms and conditions applied.</small></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Image Carousel - welcome section -->
  <div id="welcomeSection">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="slogan">airM&M is for everybody.</h2>
      <p>Make you feel welcome wherever you go, always here for you wherever you are.</p>

      <hr class="hr-dark">

      <div id="carouselSlides" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ul class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#carouselSlides" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          <li data-target="#carouselSlides" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        </ul>
        <!-- image items -->
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="carousel-images d-block w-100" src="./images/people-collage1.jpg">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Travel alone or with your beloved ones</h5>
              <p>airM&M is for everybody.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Travel for work or on a vacation</h5>
              <p>airM&M is for everybody.</p>
            </div>
            <img class="carousel-images d-block w-100" src="./images/people-collage2.jpg">

          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselSlides" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselSlides" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- video information-->
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center text-center">
      <h2 class="title">What does an airM&M look like?</h2>
    </div>

    <hr class="hr-dark">

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-6">
        <h5>Get started planning your next trip</h5>
        <p>Have a look at "TOP 5 airM&Ms" by Youtuber Levi Kelly</p>
        <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
          <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/U2MAYcQyHnQ"
            allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-6">
        <h5>Finding an unique place for your vacation?</h5>
        <p>Like an airM&M shipping container home? Yes!!</p>
        <div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9">
          <iframe class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/InjEoqcRfkY"
            allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Covid-19 -->
  <div class="container pt-0">
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center text-center">
      <h2 class="title">COVID-19 safety practices</h2>
    </div>

    <hr class="hr-dark">

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-6">
        <h5>What are the health and safety requirements for airM&M stays?
        </h5>
      </div>

      <div class="col-6">
        <p>During the COVID-19 pandemic, it’s important to keep health and safety in mind. We’ve created a set of
          mandatory COVID-19 safety practices for both for hosts and guests of airM&M listings, based on guidance from
          the <a href="https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019">World Health Organization</a>
          and the US Centers for Disease Control. In addition, you should be familiar with
          general health and safety guidelines for COVID-19 safety, continue to monitor applicable <a
            href="https://www.airbnb.ca/help/topic/1418/government-travel-restrictions-and-advisories">government travel
            restrictions and advisories</a>, and follow all national and local guidelines.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-6">
        <h5>Has airM&M followed any COVID-19 health and safety guidelines?</h5>
      </div>

      <div class="col-6">
        <p>
          airM&M has introduced guidelines and programs to help address health and safety concerns, but these measures
          cannot eliminate all risk. Especially if you're in a higher risk category (e.g. people above the age of 65 or
          people with pre-existing medical conditions such as diabetes or heart disease), we recommend obtaining
          professional guidance and taking extra precautions when you are making the decision to book a stay or an
          experience on airM&M. Learn more about <a
            href="https://www.airbnb.ca/help/article/2806/what-are-the-health-and-safety-guidelines-for-guests-on-experiences-in-reopened-regions">health
            and safety guidelines for airM&M Experiences</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- pop up Upload host listing -->
  {{> hostListingForm}}

  <!-- pop up sign up -->
  {{> signUpForm}}

  <!-- pop up log in -->
  {{> logInForm}}
  <!-- Footer -->
  {{> footer}}

</body>

</html>